Author: myEDNOSaccount
Text: Sounds like an ED yes  HRT makes people gain weight at the start and it really triggered me when i started HRT

Author: ashaed31
Text: You should definitely take your therapist's advice then. They only have your best interest at heart, and as much as it pains you to gain weight, weight loss goals should never be prioritized over health. I'm also struggling with this, and I wish it was easier to give this advice to myself.
